# React TypeScript Project

This is a React TypeScript project using webpack, yarn, and Node 20.

## Directory Structure

- `src/components/` - React UI components
- `src/containers/` - Container components (connect components to state/logic)
- `src/api/` - API functions for backend communication
- `src/utils/` - Utility functions, hooks, and helpers
- `public/` - Static assets
- `cypress/` - E2E tests

## Common Scripts

- `yarn start` - Development server (localhost:3000)
- `yarn build` - Production build
- `yarn lint` / `yarn lint:fix` - Linting
- `yarn format` / `yarn format:check` - Code formatting

## Important

Always run `nvm use` before yarn operations (Node 20 required).
